<!DOCTYPE HTML><title>Rate Limited - Liquipedia</title><meta charset=utf-8><meta name=viewport content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><style type=text/css>body{margin:40px auto;max-width:700px;line-height:1.6;font-size:18px;color:#444;padding:0 10px}h1{line-height:1.2}.reason{display:none}</style><script src=https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js></script><h1>Rate Limited</h1><p>Your IP address has been temporarily blocked from accessing Liquipedia due to excessive or invalid requests. This may happen if you're using a scraper / bot or otherwise accessing pages too quickly. Scrapers and similar tools are not permitted to access Liquipedia - please see <a href=/api-terms-of-use>the Liquipedia API terms of use</a> for information on how to access to Liquipedia data in a supported manner. Rate limiting may also be triggered by the following:<ul><li>Free VPN apps or browser extensions<li>Outdated or unsupported / obsolete browsers<li>A dynamic / shared IP address that was rate limited by someone else<li>VPN services or similar proxies<li>Corporate firewalls / content scanners<li>Malware on your PC or network</ul><p>You can visit <a href=https://check.labs.greynoise.io/ >GreyNoise IP Check</a> to check if your IP was seen acting maliciously (this may indicate you have malware or compromised devices on your network). If you still aren't sure why you were rate limited, please <a href=https://discord.gg/liquipedia>contact us on Discord</a>.<p>To restore access to Liquipedia, please complete this CAPTCHA:<form method=post action=/unblock><input type=hidden name=r id=r><div class=cf-turnstile data-sitekey=0x4AAAAAADAxD9-97WcOh5Zf></div><br><label><input type=checkbox name=agree value=1> I agree to follow the <a href=/api-terms-of-use>Liquipedia API terms of use</a></label><br><input type=submit value=Unblock></form><p><p>Note that unblocking your IP is not a permanent fix; you may still be rate limited again if you do not change whatever caused you to be blocked. <strong>Repeated triggering of rate limits may result in them becoming permanent.</strong></p><script>document.getElementById('r').value = window.location.href;</script><!-- If you are unable to open a browser because this is a server IP, run "curl https://liquipedia.net/token/generate" to receive an unblock URL. -->